msgstr "sample :drum_cymbal_open, attack: 0.01, sustain: 0, release: 0.1"

#: 03.4-Enveloped-Samples.md:117
msgid ""
"You can then emulate hitting the cymbal and then dampening it by increasing th"
"e sustain period:"
